    <section xml:id="AsymmetricalPeriod">
        <title>The Asymmetrical Period</title>
        <p>Asymmetrical periods consist of three or five phrases. In an asymmetrical period, there will be an unequal number of antecedents and consequents, hence the <q>asymmetry.</q> In the example below, there is one antecedent and two consequents.</p>
