    <section xml:id="Elision">
        <title>The Elision</title>
        <p>An <term>elision</term><idx><h>elision</h></idx> is a special device for joining phrases together in an overlapping manner. In an elision, the final bar of one phrase is simultaneously the first bar of the next phrase.</p>
